# TaskFlow Kubernetes Secrets Template
# 
# SECURITY WARNING: This is a template file with placeholder values.
# 
# For production deployment:
# 1. Copy this file to secrets.yaml
# 2. Replace all placeholder values with actual credentials
# 3. Consider using external secret management tools like:
#    - Kubernetes External Secrets Operator
